{"tid":2274430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「亞洲糖王」郭鶴年兒子郭孔華獲委任港大校董 曾偕兄姐捐30萬為林鄭助選","createTime":"2020-11-06T12:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T14:46:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e53ec8955f2a70e52aa711a259748ea3459edd4","tid":2274430,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:10:04.000Z","msg":"港大再有人事變動。政府今日（6日）刊憲，身兼港大校監的特首林鄭月娥委任馬來西亞富商郭鶴年之子、嘉里建設副主席兼行政總裁郭孔華為港大校董，任期3年，今年12月1日起生效。翻查資料，郭孔華曾在2017年偕同兄姐，合共為林鄭月娥捐款30萬元助選。港大學生會會長葉芷琳形容委任如同宣告政權進一步入侵校園。她稱校董會實權不大，但擔心郭日後若被選入校委會，將參與大學決策。<br />\n<br />\n人稱「亞洲糖王」的馬來西亞富商、嘉里物流創辦人郭鶴年，曾為林鄭月娥競選辦的資深顧問團成員。他的3名子女，包括郭孔華、郭惠光及時任香格里拉酒店集團主席郭孔丞，三人各自捐出最高限額的10萬元予林鄭助選。郭孔華翌年亦曾以代表團成員身份隨林鄭訪京「面聖」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥同時再度委任馮氏零售集團董事總經理馮詠儀，及香港寧波同鄉會會長李本俊為港大校董。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/ZNXUZT7KIJCOLIILUFGUMHXW2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FZNXUZT7KIJCOLIILUFGUMHXW2Y%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9nXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=b97f5666\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FZNXUZT7KIJCOLIILUFGUMHXW2Y%2F&h=875ee7ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/ZNXUZT7KIJCOLIILUFGUMHXW2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"18bc6daa6ab8b28d5f23d2a1d649395a30909611","tid":2274430,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f5c28bfa8e24b5eb992a8a1cc22c9d17d888d3","tid":2274430,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}